'''乔舒亚·奥本海默'''（{{lang-en|Joshua Lincoln Oppenheimer}}，{{bd|1974年|9月23日||}}）是一位[[美国|美国]]电影导演<ref>{{cite news|last1=Benzine|first1=Adam|title=“Killing,” “Square,” “20 Feet” among 2014 Oscar nominees|url=http://realscreen.com/2014/01/16/killing-square-20-feet-among-2014-oscar-nominees/|accessdate=2 September 2014|work=Realscreen|date=16 January 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140907133240/http://realscreen.com/2014/01/16/killing-square-20-feet-among-2014-oscar-nominees/|archive-date=2014-09-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，主要活跃于[[丹麦|丹麦]][[哥本哈根|哥本哈根]]<ref>[http://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/jun/20/joshua-oppenheimer-act-of-killing "They're desperately trying to run away from the reality of what they've done," says Oppenheimer, a 38-year-old Harvard graduate now based in Copenhagen] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/jun/20/joshua-oppenheimer-act-of-killing |date=20210416222315 }} The Guardian</ref><ref>[http://bombsite.com/issues/1000/articles/6992 Interview with Joshua Oppenheimer "Originally hailing from Texas, Joshua Oppenheimer now makes his home in Copenhagen, Denmark"] {{Wayback|url=http://bombsite.com/issues/1000/articles/6992 |date=20140106041025 }} Bomblog</ref>。

== 經歷 ==

奥本海默生于[[得克萨斯州|得克萨斯州]][[奥斯汀|奥斯汀]]，成长于[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]和[[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]]的Santa Fe。先后获得了[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]电影制作艺术学学位，以及[[中央聖馬丁藝術與設計學院|中央聖馬丁藝術與設計學院]]的博士学位。 

2012年执导的[[纪录片|纪录片]]《[[杀戮演绎|杀戮演绎]]》入围[[奥斯卡最佳纪录片|奥斯卡最佳纪录片]]。2014年的《[[沉默之像|沉默之像]]》获得了[[第71届威尼斯影展|第71届威尼斯影展]]评委会大奖<ref >{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/14/0907/02/A5GO9IMG00031H2L.html |language= |title=《寒枝雀静》擒威尼斯金狮 《闯入者》颗粒无收 |publisher=网易娱乐 |date=2014-09-07 |accessdate= |archive-date=2014-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140907083009/http://ent.163.com/14/0907/02/A5GO9IMG00031H2L.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并再次入围奥斯卡最佳纪录片。

